Ghana Reaps a Record Main Cocoa Crop of 903,646 Metric Tons, Board Says

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-05-30T15:11:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/ghana-reaps-a-record-main-cocoa-crop-of-903-646-metric-tons-board-says.html
Ghana reaped a record 903,646 metric
tons of cocoa in its main growing season, the Ghana Cocoa Board
said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  